MINDY [ON PHONE]:
Hello.

02:47.668 --> 02:49.877
RONNIE [WHISPERING]:
Hey, Mindy. Is this Mindy?

02:50.087 --> 02:52.922
MINDY: This is she.
- Hi, it's Ronnie.

02:53.131 --> 02:54.674
Ronnie Haxon.

02:54.883 --> 02:56.801
Wow, Mindy, how are you?

02:56.969 --> 02:58.803
[TOILET FLUSHES]

02:59.680 --> 03:01.556
MINDY:
Where are you? Are you okay?

03:01.723 --> 03:05.017
