03:40.637 --> 03:41.721
[SIGHS]

03:43.932 --> 03:45.391
Your apartment's awesome.

03:45.559 --> 03:47.602
[SOBBING]
Thanks.

03:50.898 --> 03:52.648
- Are you okay?
- I'm sorry.

03:52.816 --> 03:56.527
Uh, you wanna call your dad and see
if he can come and get you. Because...

03:56.737 --> 03:58.821
DAMON:
I came here to ask you something.

03:59.448 --> 04:02.450
Can you, like, make me a better poet?

04:02.659 --> 04:06.579
You know, like, be my mentor?

04:07.915 --> 04:11.834
