- No one deserves to be hit with a belt.

04:31.688 --> 04:33.814
You invited me to your poetry thing...

04:34.024 --> 04:36.859
...and you helped me
when I was tripping out on pot scones...

04:37.069 --> 04:40.696
...and I thought I was a fetus. So you hit
one lady over the head with a belt.

04:40.906 --> 04:42.490
So what?

04:42.658 --> 04:43.699
[SIGHS]

04:43.909 --> 04:46.994
You changed my life.

04:48.372 --> 04:51.332
Do you remember
the first time that we met?

04:51.625 --> 04:53.584
You told me that I was funny.

04:54.336 --> 04:58.756
I always thought that I was funny,
but no one ever said it before.

05:00.008 --> 05:06.347
It's like we're in Michigan
and everyone else here is the same.

05:07.140 --> 05:08.933
Except you.

05:10.227 --> 05:11.894
[WHINES]

05:27.744 --> 05:30.621
Well, Ron, that's the thing
about marriage.

05:30.831 --> 05:34.000
