05:34.209 --> 05:36.544
Chicken and mole.

05:37.546 --> 05:39.547
Man, on your big night. Ouch.

05:39.756 --> 05:41.674
That's rough.

05:42.801 --> 05:45.094
I'm gonna get some beef jerky.
You want something?

05:45.303 --> 05:46.887
- No thanks.
- Come on.

05:47.097 --> 05:50.057
Rice Krispie Treat, Twix bar, nothing?

05:50.267 --> 05:53.686
- Maybe a Twix bar.
- All right.

06:01.111 --> 06:05.489
I didn't invite him to come with me.
He just... He invited himself.

06:05.699 --> 06:07.658
Oh, sure.

06:08.952 --> 06:11.037
I'm sorry she left you stranded.

06:11.246 --> 06:13.497
It's an awful thing to do.

06:14.041 --> 06:15.916
To leave like that.

06:16.126 --> 06:18.169
Just walk out.

06:19.004 --> 06:21.213
I'll be okay.

06:25.969 --> 06:27.928
But in a way...

06:28.138 --> 06:30.181
